And we're working here
and a lot of places

00:11:10.450 --> 00:11:15.950
Upstate, kind of Nyack area
and other surrounding areas.

00:11:15.950 --> 00:11:18.160
ALAN SEALES: So the
city that the story's

00:11:18.160 --> 00:11:20.085
set in, totally fictional.

00:11:20.085 --> 00:11:21.960
JESSICA BIEL: No, it's
not totally fictional.

